    "body": "## Problem Description\r\nThe current RMS PreNorm implementation has an issue in the backward pass computation.\r\n​​Forward pass:​​\r\n```\r\nres_out = residual + x\r\nout = norm(res_out)\r\n```\r\n​​Expected backward pass:​​\r\n```\r\ndres_out = dres_out + dout * dnorm(out)  # Accumulate gradients\r\ndx = dres_out\r\n```\r\n​​Current incorrect implementation:​​\r\n```\r\ndres_out = (dres_out + dout) * dnorm(out)  # Wrong: addition before normalization\r\n```\r\n## Changes Made\r\n​​Fixed backward pass logic​​ to properly accumulate gradients according to standard backpropagation rules\r\n​​Add tests​​ to verify gradient computation correctness",
    "created_at": "2025-10-29T06:58:01Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-10-30T00:45:20Z",
